Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Ridgehill Professional Building is 32,176 SF in the prominent Minnetonka/Plymouth area. Ridgehill offers monument signage availability, ample parking, and a close proximity to highway 394 and 494.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Ridgehill - For Sale and For Lease!

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Carlson Center East is a three-story, 82,000 SF building that offers a unique setting in Carlson Center, located on Chesire Lane. Carlson Center East offers the amenities of Carlson Center while offering its own identity within the park. Generous surface parking and abundant indoor parking sets this building apart. The east side of the building overlooks a pond while the south side overlooks a wetlands area. The amenities feature: underground parking, exercise facility, access to scenic trail system, on-campus ownership, nearby restaurants and shopping.
Two Carlson Parkway is a 130,000 SF, 4-story building located adjacent to the Carlson Inn & Suites and features a main building lobby with a fireplace that overlooks a natural wetland setting.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: The 601 Tower is one of the twin towers of Carlson Center. Its striking exterior flame-cut, polished burgundy granite is complemented by reflective glass and a stepped, lighted rooftop. The beautifully landscaped grounds with their gardens, walking paths and amphitheater provide a truly unique setting for your business.
